data: {"name":"design_custom_agent","arguments":{"description":"Create a RemediationAgent that executes automated fixes for security incidents based on ForensicsAgent findings. It: 1) Reads the investigation report and recommended remediation, 2) For P2-P4 incidents, auto-executes predefined runbooks (restart deployments, scale services, rotate secrets), 3) For P1 incidents, requires human approval before executing, 4) Verifies the fix by checking system health post-remediation, 5) Links the executed runbook to the incident, 6) Resolves or escalates the incident based on outcome. Tools needed: runbook_quick_diagnostics, incident_resolve, incident_escalate, incident_link_runbook, incident_close, kubernetes_restart, kubernetes_scale. Framework: LangGraph StateGraph with human-in-the-loop interrupt for P1 incidents.","framework":"langgraph","tools":"runbook_quick_diagnostics,incident_resolve,incident_escalate,incident_link_runbook,incident_close,kubernetes_restart,kubernetes_scale"},"toolCallId":"toolu_bdrk_012AqS59Ry4KPFCzn6i6qYa7","targetServer":"openagentic_agent_architect","timestamp":"2026-02-21T00:45:04.519Z"}

